Feature: Validate downtime sessions

  Scenario Outline: Verify total session count and duration match with summary cards
  When the user clicks on the profile icon
  Then verify that the "Account Preferences" screen is displayed
  When the user clicks on the "Machines" feature
  Then verify that the user is navigated to the machines list screen
  When the user selects the machine "<machineName>" and clicks on it
  Then verify that the user is navigated to the machine information "<machineName>" screen
  When the user clicks on the "Downtime" section
  Then verify that the user is navigated to the downtime summary screen "Machine > Downtime > Summary"
  When the user fetches the sum of all status card durations
  And the user fetches the sum of all session record durations
  Then verify that the total duration sum of all status cards equals the total session duration sum

  Examples:
    | machineName     |
    | Tube Mill 1     |
    | Tube Mill 2     |
    | Tube Mill 3     |
